dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Willie Johnson. May I please have your name?
Nice to meet you, Deborah. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Of course, my policy number is five eight two four six.
Thank you. Additionally, can you confirm your date of birth so I can access your account details?
I was born on the twelfth of August, nineteen eighty seven.
Great, thank you for confirming, Deborah. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Could you please provide me with the make and model of the vehicle you'd like to add?
Thank you for the information, Deborah. I will go ahead and update your policy with the new vehicle. Thank you for your time today.
Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
